    "@value" : "Marchand, P., Risser, N., Petit, E. & Garel, M. (2025). Data from: Disturbance by massive sporting events in mountain areas: when and where matters for the protected Alpine ibex Capra ibex [Data set]. Zenodo. https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.17052197"
  } ],
