  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "These R data files contains the data needed to replicate the analyses presented in Marchand et al. 2025  - Disturbance by massive sporting events in mountain areas: when and where matters for the protected Alpine ibex Capra ibex, published in People & Nature. 'locs_export' contains gps locations, whereas 'act_export' contains activity data from gps collars. See Methods for details."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
